dc_title_s: Lotharingia septentrionalis Loraine: vers le Sept.ion.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Title cartouche includes three faces. From "Atlantis maioris appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 36 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain.
